text: Hey <@U0260V1BX> I'm working on the home page and I'm trying to architect layout so the animations work. Do you have any wires/mockups of what should move. I looked at the examples but their layout is a bit different give the variety of layout sections on the homepage.

Let me know if you need help with that.
yes. I can do that. I think that some of the icons will change based on their new content, so when i re-export i'll make SVGs
So i did give you a mockup of what should move on the homepage, although you may not have seen it. let me get you the file path again
clients/TrapIt/Trapit Website 2014/ Assets to Gaston/PDF DOCUMENTATION/HOMEPAGE ANIMATIONS.pdf
Oh, sorry I missed that. Everything looks good. The only one I'm not sure about is sliding from the bottom of the page. Will need to test what happens when people scroll fast.
ok, if we can't do it that's fine. happy to go with whatever is easy to accomplish
